The next challenge is /hotpotato 🔥 🥔 the 7 remaining players will start passing the 🥔 among themselves and whomever is at the top of the leaderboard at 11 am ET tomorrow wins immunity!

There will be mandatory and optional breaks -- pass the potato to prof to start a 2 hour break. The fun starts at noon ET.

Feature: Mutual follows for DC Requests

Warpcast now shows mutual follows in your requests inbox. This makes it easier to find people you may want to respond to.

Frame devs: we're experimenting with a slim embed for frames, starting with QCs.

For now we're rendering some defaults:
- Image from frame image
- Title from og:title
- CTA button from your frame if there's just one and it's short, otherwise "View"

Spec coming soon to give you more control. Until then, set these!
